# UI

- Tokens: `hae-crimson`, `hae-ink`, `hae-slate`, `hae-mist`, `hae-line`, `font-display`.
- Shells: Tracker `Layout`; other apps `ModuleShell`; public EiR `PublicShell`.
- Forms/popups: `@hae/ui` `Modal`.
- Nav icons: `packages/ui/src/navIcons.jsx`.
- Help: `packages/ui/src/helpContent.js`.
